author: wn.com
title: White House searches for 'single-issue voters' on gun rights
text: The Obama administration wants voters across the country to only weigh gun rights and gun-safety legislation when considering who to support, saying it's necessary for proponents of new firearms restrictions to show the same passion Second Amendment activists are known for. White House press secretary Josh Earnest told reporters Monday ... ...
